    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the 996.2 generation, presented in showroom condition. Powered by the 3.6L M96/03 flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, the engine delivers linear power through a precise G96/01 6-speed manual transaxle. The wide-body chassis retains its factory structural rigidity, supported by the original Carrera 4S suspension geometry and 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers. This unit features a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a clean bore-scope inspection, ensuring mechanical longevity. The exterior finish remains flawless with consistent paint meter readings across all panels, while the interior leather shows zero bolster wear. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
