    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade example that can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original showroom luster. The exterior paint is flawless, free of stone chips or swirl marks, and has been treated with a multi-stage paint correction followed by a premium ceramic coating that provides a deep, liquid-like mirror finish. Every body panel is original with factory-perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear and still carry that distinct new-car scent. All interior plastics, switchgear, and digital displays function perfectly with no fading or scratches. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, binder-organized service history documenting every fluid flush and inspection performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage is remarkably dry and free of any surface corrosion. Included in the sale are all original keys, the owner\u2019s manual in its leather case, and the window sticker. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated piece of automotive history for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
